name: Hunter Mastery Slate
description: Struck to recognize your achievement in reaching the rank of 13 - Hunter.

languages.description: Geschaffen, um dein Erreichen von Rang 13 - Jäger zu ehren.
languages.name: Meisterschaft-Insignie: Jäger

languages.description: Gravée pour commémorer votre réussite en atteignant le Palier 13 - Chasseur.
languages.name: Ardoise de Maîtrise - Chasseur

languages.description: Coniata per riconoscere il tuo successo nel raggiungere il grado 13 - Cacciatore.
languages.name: Targa Maestria - Cacciatore

languages.description: 랭크 13 - 헌터에 도달한 업적을 기리기 위한 표창패입니다.
languages.name: 헌터 마스터리 슬레이트

languages.description: Impresionado por reconocer tu logro al alcanzar el rango 13 - Cazador.
languages.name: Placa de Maestría de Cazador

languages.description: 为表彰你成功达到段位 13－巡猎者所打造的物品。
languages.name: 巡猎者精通石板

languages.description: ハンター「マスタリーランク13」へ到達したテンノの成果を示す表彰楯。
languages.name: ハンター マスタリー 表彰楯

languages.description: Stworzona, by upamiętnić Twój wyczyn w osiągnięciu rangi 13 - Łowca.
languages.name: Tablica Mistrzostwa Łowca

languages.description: Concedida em reconhecimento à sua conquista por alcançar o nível 13 - Caçador.
languages.name: Ardósia de Maestria: Caçador

languages.description: 篆刻來認可你達成精通段位 13－巡獵者的成就。
languages.name: 巡獵者精段匾

languages.description: ประทับตรารับรู้ถึงความสำเร็จของคุณในการไปถึงอันดับ 13 - นักล่า
languages.name: กระดานชนวนความเชี่ยวชาญ: นักล่า

languages.description: Seviye 13 - Hunter seviyesine ulaşma başarını anmak için oluşturulmuştur.
languages.name: Hunter Ustalık Plaketi
